@startuml
title OAuth 기반 회원가입

actor User
participant OAuth2LoginFilter
participant CustomOAuth2UserService
participant AuthRepository
entity Auth
participant MemberController
participant MemberService
participant AuthService
participant AuthClient
participant Email
participant AuthRepository
participant MemberRepository
participant SecurityContext

User -> OAuth2LoginFilter : GET /oauth2/authorization/kakao
OAuth2LoginFilter -> CustomOAuth2UserService : loadUser(oAuth2UserRequest)
CustomOAuth2UserService -> AuthRepository : findByProviderAndProviderUserId()
alt 존재함
  AuthRepository --> CustomOAuth2UserService : Auth
  CustomOAuth2UserService -> SecurityContext : saveAuthentication(Auth)
  OAuth2LoginFilter --> User : 로그인 성공
else 최초 로그인
  AuthRepository --> CustomOAuth2UserService : null
  CustomOAuth2UserService --> OAuth2LoginFilter : 인증은 안 됨
  OAuth2LoginFilter -> Frontend : redirect to /signup-form
end

User -> MemberController : POST /members/signup\n(accessToken, nickname, birthYear, gender)
MemberController -> MemberService : registerSocialMember(token, nickname, ...)

MemberService -> AuthClient : getSocialInfo(token)
AuthClient --> MemberService : provider, providerUserId, email

MemberService -> AuthService : registerOAuth(provider, providerUserId, email)
AuthService -> Auth : Auth.createOAuth(provider, providerUserId, rawEmail)
activate Auth
Auth -> Email : Email.of(rawEmail)
Email --> Auth : Email
deactivate Auth

AuthService -> AuthRepository : save(Auth)

MemberService -> MemberRepository : save(nickname, birthYear, gender)
MemberRepository --> MemberService : memberId

MemberService -> AuthService : linkMember(authId, memberId)
AuthService -> AuthRepository : findById(authId)
AuthService -> Auth : linkMember(memberId)
AuthService -> AuthRepository : save(Auth)

AuthService -> SecurityContext : saveAuthentication(Auth)

MemberService --> MemberController : HTTP 201 Created
@enduml